Dr. Zhang Jixian observed a group of patients with pneumonia of unknown causes on December 26th. Her hospital informed the Center for Prevention and Control of Wohan Jianghan Diseases on December 27th.
Initial genetic tests, on December 27, 2019, in samples taken from patients indicated the presence of a SARS-type coronary virus.
